{
  "id": "5abf6a6be0766600145e11d0",
  "title": "利他ではなく長期投資",
  "created": 1522494062,
  "updated": 1634840314,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "5abf6a6daff09e00007b9015",
      "text": "利他ではなく長期投資",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1522494062,
      "updated": 1522494073
    },
    {
      "id": "5abf6a70aff09e00007b9016",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/734142936045032e1cf378b94bf47c2a]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1522494064,
      "updated": 1522494064
    },
    {
      "id": "5abf6a6be0766600145e11d0",
      "text": " 将来価値の割引率は人によって違う。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1522494062,
      "updated": 1522494523
    },
    {
      "id": "5abf6b64aff09e00007b9019",
      "text": " \t図では双曲割引って書いてるけど、双曲割引は割引率自体が(非合理に)下がる話だから違う [双曲割引 - Wikipedia https://ja.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E5%8F%8C%E6%9B%B2%E5%89%B2%E5%BC%95]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1522494309,
      "updated": 1522494559
    },
    {
      "id": "5abf6babaff09e00007b901a",
      "text": "  スタンフォードの[マシュマロ実験] [マシュマロ実験 - Wikipedia https://ja.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E3%83%9E%E3%82%B7%E3%83%A5%E3%83%9E%E3%83%AD%E5%AE%9F%E9%A8%93]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1522494379,
      "updated": 1522494426
    },
    {
      "id": "5abf6b48aff09e00007b9018",
      "text": " 割引率が高い人は、今の1万円とつりあう未来の価値をより高く見積もる",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1522494281,
      "updated": 1522494578
    },
    {
      "id": "5abf6c71aff09e00007b901b",
      "text": "  なので色々な選択肢の中から「今欲しい」を選びがち",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1522494578,
      "updated": 1522494600
    },
    {
      "id": "5abf6c88aff09e00007b901c",
      "text": " 割引率がある程度低くなると、人や株式の平均的な成長率の方が大きくなる",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1522494600,
      "updated": 1522494625
    },
    {
      "id": "5abf6ca1aff09e00007b901d",
      "text": " \tそうなると、",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1522494625,
      "updated": 1522494654
    },
    {
      "id": "5abf6cbdaff09e00007b901e",
      "text": "  \tいま現金を得るより株式で長期投資した方がいい",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1522494654,
      "updated": 1522494657
    },
    {
      "id": "5abf6cc1aff09e00007b901f",
      "text": "   今自分が利益を得るよりも他人に利益を与える方がいい ([返報性]を仮定)",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1522494657,
      "updated": 1522494671
    },
    {
      "id": "5abf6a9baff09e00007b9017",
      "text": "\t自分の将来利益を最大化する利己的な判断の結果「自分が取るより他人に与える」という行動が生まれる",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1522494108,
      "updated": 1522494717
    },
    {
      "id": "5abf6cfcaff09e00007b9021",
      "text": " \tこれが一見[利他]的行動に見える",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1522494717,
      "updated": 1522494728
    },
    {
      "id": "5abf6d0caff09e00007b9022",
      "text": "  しかし実際は単なる[長期投資]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1522494733,
      "updated": 1522494741
    },
    {
      "id": "5abf6ce8aff09e00007b9020",
      "text": "\tどちらかのかの識別",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1522494696,
      "updated": 1522494772
    },
    {
      "id": "5abf6d34aff09e00007b9024",
      "text": " \tなんらかの理由によって相手の将来[成長率]が低い場合",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1522494772,
      "updated": 1522494832
    },
    {
      "id": "5abf6d4aaff09e00007b9025",
      "text": "  \t利他は将来成長など関係ないので影響を受けないはず",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1522494794,
      "updated": 1522494802
    },
    {
      "id": "5abf6d52aff09e00007b9026",
      "text": "   長期投資は影響を受ける",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1522494802,
      "updated": 1522494822
    },
    {
      "id": "6171aef2aff09e0000bdd05c",
      "text": "   関連 [メンターの個性#60363486aff09e0000b3a450]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1634840307,
      "updated": 1634840314
    },
    {
      "id": "5ac0b7a7aff09e000059ea06",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1522579368,
      "updated": 1522579368
    },
    {
      "id": "5ac0b7a7aff09e000059ea05",
      "text": " [信頼と株式]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1522579368,
      "updated": 1522579400
    },
    {
      "id": "5abf6d30aff09e00007b9023",
      "text": "　[長期的]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1522494768,
      "updated": 1622392529
    },
    {
      "id": "60b3becbaff09e00007cea50",
